{"id":343,"date":"2022-05-22T15:55:07","date_gmt":"2022-05-22T15:55:07","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/soncovax.com\/?p=343"},"modified":"2024-11-17T09:56:31","modified_gmt":"2024-11-17T09:56:31","slug":"9-cach-lam-dep-cho-moi-khong-gian-song-trong-nha-ban","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/9-cach-lam-dep-cho-moi-khong-gian-song-trong-nha-ban\/","title":{"rendered":"9 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng trong nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c<strong>\u00a0l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda<\/strong>\u00a0lu\u00f4n mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi cho ch\u00fang ta, m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf ngo\u00e0i kia nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t khi m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian trong nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0i tr\u00ed \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch th\u00ec b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<\/p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>&#8220;C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i <strong>c\u00e1ch\u00a0l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng<\/strong> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o thu h\u00fat cho m\u1ecdi c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c.&#8221;<\/p>\r\n<\/blockquote>\r\n<p>M\u1ed9t ch\u00fat s\u1eafc m\u00e0u, m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat ho\u1ea1 ti\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t n\u00e9t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0\u00a0<strong>9 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng trang tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng<\/strong>\u00a0gi\u00fap l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n:<\/p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"1-lua-chon-mau-sac-khong-gian-song\">1. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng<\/span><\/h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-646099211\"> \n\t<div id=\"col-469430600\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\r\n<p>D\u00f9 nh\u1eefng c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111i\u1ec3m xuy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00f4 bi\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t trang t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac th\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 h\u00e0i ho\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 draf gi\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng s\u00e1ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c t\u00f4ng xanh \u2013 t\u00edm \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u01b0a c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.<\/p>\r\n<p>T\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm cho t\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1eb9o \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1edbi m\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t \n\t<div id=\"col-182612312\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1632096389\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-01.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-01.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-01-450x600.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1632096389 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t \t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t <\/div>\r\n<h2><span id=\"2-dung-guong\">2. D\u00f9ng g\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/span><\/h2>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1748971889\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-02.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-02.jpg 750w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-02-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1748971889 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 tr\u00f4ng r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n th\u00ec b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi cho m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.\u00a0<strong>Trang tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng<\/strong>\u00a0b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t hay nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n. M\u1eabu ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho th\u1ea5y g\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. B\u1ed1 tr\u00ed m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1edbn ngay ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c x\u00e9o t\u1eeb c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng (c\u1ea3 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 nh\u1ecf) v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n.<\/p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"3-bo-sung-vat-dung-cho-cac-phong\">3. B\u1ed5 sung v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng cho c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng<\/span><\/h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-552790368\"> \n\t<div id=\"col-2126045680\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\r\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0<strong>l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 trang tr\u00ed th\u00eam c\u00e1c ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian trong nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\r\n<p>M\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 r\u1ed1i trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn.<\/p>\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 gh\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea9u c\u1ea1nh b\u1ed3n t\u1eafm v\u00e0 ch\u1eadu c\u00e2y c\u1ea3nh trong nh\u00e0 nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean b\u1ed3n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u1ea5m c\u00fang h\u01a1n.<\/p>\r\n<p>Khi trang tr\u00ed v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u2013 h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n y\u00eau th\u00edch v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t \n\t<div id=\"col-973125626\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_2117734479\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"743\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-03.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-03.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-03-485x600.jpg 485w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_2117734479 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t \t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t <\/div>\r\n<h2><span id=\"4-cay-canh-trong-nha-tao-nen-su-khac-biet\">4. C\u00e2y c\u1ea3nh trong nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t<\/span><\/h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-2075506333\"> \n\t<div id=\"col-1596837299\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\r\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u00e0o v\u1ec1\u00a0<strong>\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng\u00a0trang tr\u00ed nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda<\/strong>, h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd m\u00e1ch v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean xinh \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam\u00a0c\u00e2y xanh trang tr\u00ed trong nh\u00e0\u00a0ho\u1eb7c hoa.<\/p>\r\n<p>Chi\u1ebfc b\u00e0n d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y t\u1ef1 th\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n n\u00e9t trang nh\u00e3 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ecd khuynh di\u1ec7p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt h\u01a1n. H\u00e3y l\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1eadu c\u00e2y tr\u1ed3ng trong nh\u00e0, hoa theo m\u00f9a ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ch\u1eadu c\u00e2y d\u1ea1ng treo kh\u00e1c. Chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng cho nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t \n\t<div id=\"col-1417547910\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_214395973\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-04.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-04.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-04-400x600.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_214395973 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t \t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t <\/div>\r\n<h2><span id=\"5-tan-dung-anh-sang-tu-nhien\">5. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/span><\/h2>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_979972737\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1020\" height=\"764\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-05-1024x767.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-05-1024x767.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-05-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-05-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-05.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_979972737 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u\u00a0<strong>\u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean trong nh\u00e0<\/strong>\u00a0th\u00ec c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee3i g\u00ec m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. \u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u1ea5m \u00e1p v\u00e0 tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng h\u01a1n. Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn hai khung c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1eeb s\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho c\u1ea3 c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng. D\u00f9 nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean hay \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean ng\u00f3 ng\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c khung c\u1eeda s\u1ed5. Ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng\u00a0<strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong>\u00a0v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc th\u1eadt ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n, c\u1ea3 c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i theo c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"6-dung-ngai-trai-nghiem\">6. \u0110\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m<\/span><\/h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1146362182\"> \n\t<div id=\"col-1852674660\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\r\n<p>M\u1ecdi ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chung m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m: s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<\/p>\r\n<p>Ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7y ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t mua v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian \u1ee9ng \u00fd h\u01a1n, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.<\/p>\r\n<p>M\u1eabu ph\u00f2ng \u0103n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5i bay c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf \u0103n\u00a0\u0111i k\u00e8m m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec7m ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7y ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t \n\t<div id=\"col-531581135\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_517950198\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-06.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-06.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-06-400x600.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_517950198 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t \t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t <\/div>\r\n<h2><span id=\"7-lam-moi-gach-op\">7. L\u00e0m m\u1edbi g\u1ea1ch \u1ed1p<\/span><\/h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-273162142\"> \n\t<div id=\"col-1948107304\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\r\n<p>Trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm ho\u1eb7c ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n, g\u1ea1ch \u1ed1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n\u00a0<strong>l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho b\u1ebfp<\/strong>\u00a0nh\u00e0 m\u00ecnh th\u00ec h\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea1ch \u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<\/p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp phong c\u00e1ch Scandinavian tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00e0y n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt h\u01a1n nh\u1edd v\u00e0o g\u1ea1ch \u1ed1p b\u1ebfp m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n ngay tr\u00ean t\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\r\n<p>T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u01b0 s\u00e0n nh\u00e0, g\u1ea1ch \u1ed1p, s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<\/p>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t \n\t<div id=\"col-717197745\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1602163303\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-07.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-07.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-07-400x600.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1602163303 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t \t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t <\/div>\r\n<h2><span id=\"8-them-cac-hoa-tiet-trang-tri\">8. Th\u00eam c\u00e1c h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed<\/span><\/h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1537840341\"> \n\t<div id=\"col-1144572980\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\r\n<p>T\u1eeb th\u1ea3m tr\u1ea3i s\u00e0n c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn, g\u1ed1i trang tr\u00ed sofa hay m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m ch\u0103n \u1ea5m \u00e1p, nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb v\u1ea3i b\u1ed1, s\u1ee3i \u0111an n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, ai l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u00eam \u00e1i, m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i t\u1eeb t\u1ea5m th\u1ea3m d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n?.<\/p>\r\n<p>M\u1eabu ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch \u2013 c\u00e2y xanh, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u2013 nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5m th\u1ea3m c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb\u00a0phong c\u00e1ch B\u1eafc \u00c2u\u00a0ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 khi\u1ebfn c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n.<\/p>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t \n\t<div id=\"col-1518418857\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t \t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_740098781\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"870\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-08.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-08.jpg 600w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-08-414x600.jpg 414w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_740098781 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t \t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t <\/div>\r\n<h2><span id=\"9-tranh-viec-bua-bon\">9. Tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c b\u1eeba b\u1ed9n<\/span><\/h2>\r\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1838855924\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-09.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-09.jpg 750w, https:\/\/sonvinalux.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/meo-lam-dep-nha-khong-gian-song-09-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1838855924 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\r\n<p>Ai c\u0169ng s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u0103n b\u1ebfp hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i n\u00e0y v\u00ec thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n xinh \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a n\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 cho c\u0103n b\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u00e0i ph\u00fat d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 mang l\u1ea1i cho b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu. K\u1ec7 b\u1ebfp n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfm qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng gian b\u1ebfp nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n. Trong b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0o, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ch\u1ed7 c\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c cho \u0111i nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng\u00a0c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0\u00a0hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.<\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda lu\u00f4n mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi cho ch\u00fang ta, m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf ngo\u00e0i kia nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t khi m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian trong nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0i tr\u00ed \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch th\u00ec b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y \u011